Si kastaba ha ahaatee, dadaal lagu soo saaro xasiloonida dadweynaha lama sameynin ilaa 19ka Janaayo 2020, markii madaxa Xarunta Xakamaynta Cudurrada Wuhan uu ku dhawaaqay in fayraska cusub uu leeyahay awood u yar oo uu ku gudbiyo dadka si wax ku ool ah, isla markaana uu leeyahay awood u yar oo lagu hortago cudurka.
Fariintan ayaa sababtay in digniinta dadweynaha aan loo qaadan si dhab ah, gaar ahaan iyadoo dalka oo dhan uu isu diyaarinayay in la qabto xafladaha guga ee sanadka cusub, taas oo lumisay fursad muhiim ah oo looga hortago faafitaanka cudurka ee baaxadda ugu yar ee Wuhan.
Hay'adaha xakamaynta cudurka ee Shiinaha ayaa laga yaabaa inay bartaan casharkaan adag waxayna sameyn doonaan horumarro muhiim ah oo ku saabsan tallaabooyinka mustaqbalka.
Tusaale ahaan, hay'adahaasi waa inay (1) ka taxaddaraan wargelinta dadweynaha maxaa yeelay wax kasta oo ay sheeganayaan ayaa la soo bandhigi doonaa dadweynaha oo isbeddeli kara aragtidooda iyo go'aannadooda; (2) ay ka dareemi doonaan macluumaad aan caadi ahayn oo ka imanaya rugta caafimaadka, halkii ay sugaan warbixinnada rasmiga ah ee dhakhaatiirta ama saraakiisha masuulka ka ah; (3) ay ka sii adkeyn doonaan sidii ay u xakameyn lahaayeen cudur faafa oo iman kara marxaladaha bilowga ah halkii ay ugu yeedhi lahaayeen dadka inay xasilloonaan; (4) si joogto ah, u siiyaan macluumaad macquul ah oo wax ku ool ah oo dadweynaha u heli kara si kor loogu qaado wacyiga guud ee cudurka faafa, isla markaana ay u tijaabiyaan una hagaajiso nidaamka jawaabta bulshada.
