Bangladesh ayaa soo sheegtay shan dhimasho oo cusub oo ka dhashay COVID-19, taasoo ah tirada ugu sareysa ee hal maalin.
Shalay, Bangladesh ayaa ku dhawaaqday shan footo maalin kasta oo ay ku jirto COVID-19.
Waa tirada ugu badan ee dhimashada cudurka ee maalin kasta.
Shalay, Machadka Cudurrada, Xakamaynta iyo Cilmi-baarista Bangladesh (IEDCR) ayaa soo sheegay 114 kiis oo cudur ah iyo 33 kiis oo ka soo kabashada kaabayaasha guriga.
