"Maamulka Donald Trump ee Mareykanka ayaa ku tilmaamay coronavirus sida ""virus Shiinaha"" ama ""virus Wuhan"", isagoo sheegay in ""censorship, sabab u ah faafitaanka fayraska oo hadda noqday cudur caalami ah"" ay ku soo noqdeen dhaleeceyn qaar ka mid ah dhaleeceeyayaasha sida cunsuriyad iyo ""dhaafsiga dareenka ee ku saabsan awoodda aan dawladdiisa ku lahayn in ay xakameyso cudurka"".
Daily Beast waxay heshay shabakad khadka tooska ah oo ay ku adeegsato tallaabooyinka isgaarsiinta ee Golaha Ammaanka Qaranka, taas oo adeegsanaysa istaraatijiyad loo yaqaan ""wax walba waa ka hooseeya Shiinaha"".
