Bishii Maarso 19, 2020, Hay'adda Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ayaa ogolaansho isticmaal degdeg ah (EUA) u soo saartay Abbott Laboratories tijaabooyinka nidaamka Abbott's m2000; Hay'adda Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ayaa horay u soo saartay ogolaansho la mid ah shirkadaha Hologic, LabCorp iyo Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Bishii Maarso 21, 2020, shirkadda Cepheid ayaa sidoo kale ka heshay Ururka Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ee EUA tijaabada oo qaadan doonta 45 daqiiqo.
Hay'adda Cuntada iyo Dawooyinka ayaa ansixisay tijaabooyin ku saabsan isticmaalka tiknoolajiyada kor u qaadista isothermal nucleic acid halkii ay ka heli lahayd PCR.
Iyadoo aan loo baahnayn in la sameeyo wareegyo heerkulka isku xigta, habkan ayaa lagu ogaan karaa natiijo wanaagsan 5 daqiiqo gudahood iyo mid taban 13 daqiiqo gudahood.
